➜陇南：徽县诗人共贺徽州夜市开业大吉
http://www.sohu.com/a/414660065_804243	33234
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 在徽州夜市开业之际，徽县诗人提笔赋诗，以示祝贺，祝徽州夜市开业大吉，财源滚滚！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/cc178adeb34f41f6995de2e8c625dbae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>徽州美食街</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/子兰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徽州多美食，香溢满街中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠境人皆羡，佳肴味不同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烹调春色嫩，尝品舌尖丰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彻夜华灯灿，商机火样红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200824/1a1d851bad5c445f85977a700b2ef089.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>徽州夜市有感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/张敬年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溢彩华灯映作坊，徽州小吃美名扬。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
