<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">珍肴鲜味春风座，食客熙攘聚贾商。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200824/99871729049f4b19804e8847f80d93c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>徽州夜市(新韵)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/陇上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜市新开路自宽，小吃百品众心欢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一街古建流唐韵，满眼人潮逛地摊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/3cb045ef4e6a40239dce7ddfe1258ade.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺徽州夜市即将开业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/张国栋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场疫疾袭全球，经济萧条几度休。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两会群英齐呼吁，国家总理解民愁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顷时地摊起风浪，繁盛唐街耀九州。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美食飘香灯火夜，客商同赞党恩酬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/aac21b79fc1c4207a5c89de4b868374a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺徽州夜市开业大吉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/成小毅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霓虹光亮处，徽州夜市喧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美食尝百味，文化启金源。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200824/7d4ef3d6c53b41db8b7dbd6a8eb1c5f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>唐人街夜市</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/吴彩芹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东风吹永夜，韵古自流芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲榭人潮涌，相邀对酒觞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200824/a6cacb583baa4e0fb93c19c443de21b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>观唐街夜市</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/张泓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜市街衢傍我家，门楼彩绘见繁华。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南桥路过人如织，烤肉摊前品辣麻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200824/b37cbea3ab9c4eaba0de2f921b791e07.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（来源：文/徽县市管办 图/陇南视线）</p>
